gmoji\" /><br />\n但想讀下相關既基礎課程先<br />\n有冇巴打絲打知邊間好 兼讀既<br />\n感謝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"好似space vtc hkcc都有，邊個好就真係唔識，只可以講讀設計可以唔畫畫，有美感即可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4521a0d450bf8c2350305f28c4a0e31c7c84d0","tid":1810261,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T17:51:47.000Z","msg":"唔好讀 <br />\n死路一條"},{"pid":"9b0bd550c4c59db3117ae95107f87c14e61ee73b","tid":1810261,"uid":319606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:17:21.000Z","msg":"［借位宣傳］設計師標準工時及工會意見諮詢問卷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qer101k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQer101k.jpg&h=01cb968d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n設計師標準工時及工會意見諮詢問卷<br />\n<br />\n問卷連結：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1XxS1c3Et7RcjCitHpOG6OzG2DXRK-eUOfLC_b9VNX1U/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1XxS1c3Et7RcjCitHpOG6OzG2DXRK-eUOfLC_b9VNX1U%2Fedit&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=d3ef2802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1XxS1c3Et7RcjCitHpOG6OzG2DXRK-eUOfLC_b9VNX1U/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n問卷目的<br />\n<br />\n第一部分<br />\n根據瑞銀集團2018年《價格與收入》(<a href=\"https://www.ubs.com/microsites/prices-earnings/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ubs.com%2Fmicrosites%2Fprices-earnings%2Fen&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDj%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=220f8444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ubs.com/microsites/prices-earnings/en</a> )的研究報告顯示，香港工作人士每週平均工作時間高達52小時。而香港設計界的工時過長問題亦相當嚴重，工時規定在設計行業的勞工權益中有關鍵的作用，因此在籌備工會的階段，我們希望可以透過問卷調查了解設計界的行業現狀，以及設計人員對標準工時之看法。<br />\n<br />\n第二部分<br />\n現時工會在籌備階段，希望聽取更多設計人員的意見，令籌備工作更加完善。<br />\n<br />\n內容相當豐富，請比足心機去填寫🙇<br />\n唔好白費籌委妹妹既心血<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#問卷"},{"pid":"75892a9cf172bd16b7650a8472bc21104b03c1c8","tid":1810261,"uid":61744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T19:39:07.000Z","msg":"好辛苦啊 成日冇得瞓  人工又唔高"},{"pid":"31de9292acff1f6a31276dbc7eac53c6f92809e1","tid":1810261,"uid":14542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T20:03:31.000Z","msg":"老士講句，要有心入呢一行先好入。好多人都捱唔過，捱唔過其他工作嘅誘惑，因為當自己好努力做，做到咁上下，但人工又跟唔上，自己會考慮其他收入高嘅工作。當然，你當咗室內設計係你終生職業，你自己又喜歡的話，你會好享受自己嘅工作，甚至會好proud of 自己成為一個設計師。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 讀室內設計，做室內設計"},{"pid":"be14c2cd9976c3f4719f6af8da5445ad17ba4eab","tid":1810261,"uid":334418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:07:13.000Z","msg":"室內設計不如archi，做返室內設計又得，繼續archi路又得<br />\n<br />\n室內設計就轉5反archi要重讀"}]}